["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"会计上指无法收回的应收账款、长期借款、其它应收款等"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"呆怔"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"dāizhèng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"〈方〉∶呆住,指神经一下子失去控制而表现出呆板的样子"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"他听到这个噩耗,呆怔了好一阵子"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"呆滞"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"dāizhì","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)行动、动作或反应迟钝的"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"他那呆滞的头脑"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)无表情的"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"跳着舞,眼光呆滞,无精打采"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(3)经济上不活跃或商品、股票等滞销的"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"呆滞的市面"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"呆子"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"dāizi","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)迟钝的人"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)未成熟的或呆头呆脑的男孩或年轻人"}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【丑集上】【口字部】呆 ·康熙筆画：7　·部外筆画：4 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【篇海】補道切，同保。詳人部保字註。　又莫厚切，音母。古文某字。今俗以爲癡獃字。誤也。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"【類篇】同槑省。或作某，通作梅。【本草】梅，杏類，倒杏爲呆。俗以爲癡獃之獃，誤。　【說文】从"},{"type":"span","content":"𠙵"},{"type":"text","content":"不从口。"},{"type":"span","content":"𣏁"},{"type":"text","content":"，本字。"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"traditional":"獃","type":"通用字、常用字","pinyin":["dāi","ái"],"radical":"口","stroke":"四画","total_stroke":"七画","stroke_order":"丨フ一一丨ノ丶","input_method":{"bopomofo":"RD","number":"60904","unicode":"U+5446","wubi":"KSU"}}